However, in all the documents unveiled by Mr. Snowden, there is no indication to date that the United States has passed on trade secrets from foreign companies to American companies.
Politicians have expressed concern that the EU does not have sufficient IT and Internet capacity and believe that it should try to reduce its dependence on the US.
Business leaders are sceptical about this.
